# 🎯 Quick Demo Reference Card

---

## 🚀 Demo Flow

```
1. Introduction (2 min)
2. Login (1 min)
3. Assessment (6 min)
4. AI Analysis (5 min)
5. PDF Download (2 min)
6. Save & History (3 min)
7. Architecture (3 min)
8. Q&A (5-10 min)
```

